title: Game of Thrones Maps
description:
Several High Quality PNG images of Essos i.e. the Game of Thrones world.

These have been ripped from the "World of Ice and Fire" iOS app.  The maps are as follows:

The Known World - 10000x6667px
Westeros - 6667x10000px

Beyond the Wall - 2444x3475px
The North - 2444x3475px
The South - 2444x3475px
The Free Cities - 2444x3475px
Valyria - 2444x3475px



The first two images are the same as those from "The Lands of Ice and Fire" map set.
